341
00:19:29,539 --> 00:19:31,339
Okay, I'll do that.

342
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:34,210
What are you waiting for? Try it.

343
00:19:34,609 --> 00:19:36,250
It's really good.

344
00:19:36,549 --> 00:19:37,579
Okay.

345
00:19:39,049 --> 00:19:40,779
