What?

350
00:20:07,710 --> 00:20:08,779
Ta-da!

351
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,319
Oh, my.

352
00:20:16,890 --> 00:20:17,890
My gosh!

353
00:20:19,359 --> 00:20:21,558
