384
00:22:12,170 --> 00:22:13,440
Eat your breakfast before you go to work.

385
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:33,289
Happy birthday.

386
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,829
Why are you here so early?

387
00:22:35,859 --> 00:22:38,160
Why? I wanted to be the first one to wish you a happy birthday.

388
00:22:39,599 --> 00:22:41,029
Let's eat this and go to work together.

389
00:22:41,670 --> 00:22:43,299
