395
00:22:58,009 --> 00:23:00,319
Don't tell me you made a heart with green peas.

396
00:23:05,990 --> 00:23:07,059
You're so mean.

397
00:23:08,529 --> 00:23:09,559
Sorry.

398
00:23:11,190 --> 00:23:14,400
